description.en:
Interline Pro filter set

This Interline filter set is a low-cost filter set suitable for small and medium sized pools. The minimum pump capacity is 13 m³/hour. The air valve of the pump can be filled with fiberclean, so you always keep your pool clean.

Specifications:
Colour: black
Gender: unisex
Material: plastic
Length of hose: 2x 4.5 metres
Voltage: 230V
Minimum pump capacity: 13 m³/hour
Swimming pool capacity: 12.000 litres
Weight: 20.8 kg

Contents:
2 hoses
4 Hose clamps
1 RCD plug
1 Set fiberclean
